cts for Atomikos-managed distributed transactions, participants, and transactional resources. It also exposes recovery and logging abstractions used to coordinate two-phase commit and crash recovery.\",\nmetadata/javax.servlet.jsp/jsp-api/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"This artifact provides the JavaServer Pages 2.1 API contracts, including core JSP, tag extension, and expression language interfaces used by JSP containers and applications. It defines standard types that JSP engines and custom tag libraries implement at compile time and runtime.\",\ntests/src/org.jooq/jooq/3.18.2/src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image/tests-only/proxy-config.json:6:        \"interfaces\": [\nmetadata/org.jboss.spec.javax.interceptor/jboss-interceptors-api_1.2_spec/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"This library provides the Java EE Interceptors 1.2 API classes from JSR 318. It defines the javax.interceptor annotations and interfaces used to declare interceptor bindings and invocation contexts.\",\nmetadata/org.jboss.spec.javax.interceptor/jboss-interceptors-api_1.1_spec/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Provides the Java EE Interceptors 1.1 API classes in the javax.interceptor package. It defines the annotations and interfaces used to declare interceptor bindings and interception methods such as AroundInvoke and InvocationContext.\",\nmetadata/schemas/reachability-metadata-schema-v1.2.0.json:383:              \"title\": \"A list of interfaces defining the proxy class\",\nmetadata/schemas/reachability-metadata-schema-v1.2.0.json:402:                \"interfaces\": {\nmetadata/schemas/reachability-metadata-schema-v1.2.0.json:403:                  \"title\": \"Non-empty list of interfaces implemented by the lambda class\",\nmetadata/schemas/reachability-metadata-schema-v1.2.0.json:414:                \"interfaces\"\nmetadata/io.jsonwebtoken/jjwt-gson/0.12.0/reachability-metadata.json:222:      \"type\": \"java.security.interfaces.ECPrivateKey\"\nmetadata/io.jsonwebtoken/jjw